TITLE: Verifying WSL and WSLg Installation on Windows
DESCRIPTION: Commands to check if WSL and WSLg are properly installed on a Windows system for Docker compatibility.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/blob/main/docs/core/testing/usage-instructions.md#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
ls -a -w 1 /mnt/wslg
wsl --list --verbose
wsl --install
wsl --set-default [subsystem]
wsl --set-version [subsystem] 2
```

